Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅亡的序曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附在我身體內的靈魂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們現身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷恨的靈魂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被世界毀滅的你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪到你們來毀滅世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開新世界的大門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您打算殺死我是真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎? 女神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬龍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫查哈多魯特是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀…只要殺死查哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就不會失去親愛的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有這個辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直都是在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次要把我丟下來不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神 為什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的要殺凱洛特嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天妳一定會明白的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子們…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是在沒有父母的照顧下成長的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們變得很出色才回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我卻沒有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查哈的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏在凱洛特身體裡的破壞神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒破壞神的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那些孩子們身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四柱天神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標是隱藏在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特葛拉瑟身體裡的破壞神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來我身邊 凱洛特葛拉瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以前就講好了吧 大姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一我有什麼事情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛就麻煩妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 萬一我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的就拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這個人 他就是我們要打敗的對手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查哈多魯特…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在等你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是查哈多魯特嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的目標是大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰凱洛一根寒毛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那全看你們的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想過了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個想過了沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個到底想過了沒有?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想過什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界到底為什麼會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你們幾個全沒看見嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界變成了這個模樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你們幾個全沒看見嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠實現我夢想的人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救凱洛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬龍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大勝…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有認為能打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他簡直是毫髮無傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的功力長進了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 要讓這個城掉下去法莎特呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面有小孩子在 你知不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個答案只要你想起我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 我跟你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我跟你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前就已經認識了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們過去的所有記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被正義女神封印起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快想起來吧 孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那令人憎惡的過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那充滿不祥和善的童年記憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們早就認識我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們應該會瞭解我真正的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我也是那其中的一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己跨出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是查哈先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 您終於回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你要給我們禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 每次都只給蒂拉她們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她們兩個沒有爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是蒂拉她們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查哈先生是所有沒有父母親的小孩的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我雖然知道…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有禮物給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我可以陪你們練劍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎? 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認識…那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經跟我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起過…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼? 為什麼呢? 查哈先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒做什麼壞事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候的恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓凱洛特的力量失去控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去 凱洛…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的心靈就會破壞\N親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法再恢復人形了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛\N親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 你不能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 你要振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 剩下的就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊了 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有可怕的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 一切的恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來平息…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬…馬龍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬龍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉輪王轉世的馬龍葛拉瑟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨肉的親情是你的致命傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是脆弱的親情…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就來喚醒隱藏在你身體裡的可怕怪物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬龍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.23,0:20:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:20:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢把馬龍給殺了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是多塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人要活下去就需要有幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人認為世界的結束和誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都必須是這樣的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能轉變成實際
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.20,0:21:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現在毀滅天空中的太古城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是當時的人們所產生的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幻想轉變成現實的一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在流著黑色血的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就開始哀嚎了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆走獵人第二十五話 破壞神復活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會和世界一起滅亡嗎?

